tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE utilization_review_data (
	id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	patient_id INT,
	service_date DATE,
	service_description TEXT,
	reviewer_name TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE utilization_review_data (
  review_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  member_id UUID,
  service_date DATE,
  reviewer_name VARCHAR(50),
  service_description VARCHAR(255),
  outcome VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE member_data (
  member_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  member_name VARCHAR(50),
  dob DATE,
  address VARCHAR(100),
  phone_number VARCHAR(15)
);

CREATE TABLE utilization_reviews (
    review_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    member_id INT,
    service_date DATE,
    service_description TEXT,
    reviewer_name VARCHAR(50),
    review_outcome VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE members (
    member_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    member_name VARCHAR(100),
    member_type VARCHAR(50),
    member_dob DATE,
    member_city VARCHAR(50),
    member_state VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE services (
    service_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    service_name VARCHAR(100),
    service_category VARCHAR(50),
    service_cost DECIMAL(10,2),
    service_provider VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE providers (
    provider_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    provider_name VARCHAR(100),
    provider_specialty VARCHAR(50),
    provider_location VARCHAR(100),
    provider_contact VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE Utilization_Review_Data (
    Member_ID INT,
    Service_Date DATE,
    Service_Type VARCHAR(50),
    Provider_ID INT,
    Service_Cost DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE Member_Details (
    Member_ID INT,
    Member_Name VARCHAR(100),
    Member_DOB DATE,
    Member_Gender VARCHAR(10),
    Member_Address VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE Service_Review (
    Review_ID INT,
    Member_ID INT,
    Review_Date DATE,
    Review_Comments TEXT,
    Review_Result VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE Service_Log (
    Log_ID INT,
    Member_ID INT,
    Service_Date DATE,
    Service_Type VARCHAR(50),
    Provider_ID INT
);
